00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:15,171
# For he's a jolly good fellow #

319
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:17,504
- #Which nobody can deny #
- [Nurse] Good-bye.

320
00:21:17,575 --> 00:21:19,805
- #Which nobody can deny #
- [All Saying Good-bye]

321
00:21:19,878 --> 00:21:22,005
#Which nobody can deny ##

322
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:25,743
[Whirring]

323
00:21:29,421 --> 00:21:31,355
This kid's a little shocky.

324
00:21:31,423 --> 00:21:33,414
[Hawkeye] We'll take care of it,
Henry. You're fired.

325
00:21:33,491 --> 00:21:36,824
That's right, Henry.
Your job is finished here. Get on that chopper.

326
00:21:36,895 --> 00:21:39,227
Prep him. We'll be down in a minute.
So long, Henry.

327
00:21:39,297 --> 00:21:42,789
- Have a good trip.
- Take it easy, pal.

328
00:21:57,449 --> 00:22:00,145
You behave yourself, or I'm going
to come back and kick your butt.

329
00:22:00,218 --> 00:22:02,311
[No Audible Dialogue]

330
00:22:50,668 --> 00:22:52,363
<i>[Trapper] Radar, put a mask on.</i>

331
00:22:52,437 --> 00:22:54,869
If that's my discharge,
give it to me straight. I can take it.

332
00:22:55,003 --> 00:22:58,234
I have a message.

333
00:22:59,574 --> 00:23:04,238
[Takes Deep Breath]
Lieutenant Colonel...

334
00:23:04,312 --> 00:23:08,305
Henry Blake's plane...
[Shaky Breath]

335
00:23:08,383 --> 00:23:11,875
Was shot down over the sea ofJapan.

336
00:23:14,589 --> 00:23:16,921
It spun in.

337
00:23:19,594 --> 00:23:22,256
There were no survivors.

338
00:23:24,565 --> 00:23:27,227
[Takes Deep Breath]

339
00:23:31,472 --> 00:23:33,963
[Crying, Sniffling]

340
00:23:55,763 --> 00:23:58,755
<i>[Man On P.A.]</i>
<i>Mash 4077 bids Henry Blake...</i>

341
00:23:58,833 --> 00:24:01,996
<i>a reluctant and affectionate farewell.</i>

